                            <path d="M17.94 17.94A10.07 10.07 0 0 1 12 20c-7 0-11-8-11-8a18.45 18.45 0 0 1 5.06-5.94M9.9 4.24A9.12 9.12 0 0 1 12 4c7 0 11 8 11 8a18.5 18.5 0 0 1-2.16 3.19m-6.72-1.07a3 3 0 1 1-4.24-4.24"/>
                            <line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23"/>
                          </svg>
                        </span>
                        <span class="topic-badge reported" title="Есть жалобы">
                          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"/>
                            <line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                          </svg>
                        </span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="topic-title-wrapper">
                        <a href="#" class="topic-title">[СКРЫТО] Подозрительный контент</a>
                        <span class="topic-excerpt">Тема скрыта из-за жалоб пользователей...</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <span class="category-tag" style="--tag-color: #3b82f6;">Оффтоп</span>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <div class="author-cell">
                      <div class="author-avatar warned">X</div>
                      <span class="author-name">SuspiciousUser</span>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td class="td-stats">12</td>
                  <td class="td-stats">456</td>
                  <td class="td-date">
                    <span class="date-primary">10 Мар</span>
                    <span class="date-secondary">2024</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="td-actions">
                    <div class="action-buttons">
                      <button class="action-btn success" title="Показать" onclick="showTopic(6)">
